data.title: Research Data & Digital Scholarship Exchange (RDDSx)
data.text:
Using This Space

The RDDS unit has priority on booking the space. On- and off-campus partners with focuses on data, digital humanities, digital publishing, GIS, and more can request to book the area with the permission of RDDS. Email libraryRDDS@pobox.upenn.edu to learn more.

About RDDSx

The RDDSx is a collaborative space for the activities of the Research Data & Digital Scholarship unit and its partners on campus. We foster a community of those interested in data-driven and data-literate initiatives and digital projects.
